snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE HERE! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9

We're back with more Super Mario Maker 2! Today, Steph and I will attempt to tackle this game together. People tell me I don't play nice with others when it comes to video games, so we'll see how it goes! 

The levels we played:
Shrine of the Sacred Stiletto
First Forest Fortress
Switching Speed (hard)
A giant monster
House of Boos
A Tale of Two Yoshis
Yoshi's Egg-cellent Adventure!
Super Mario Sunshine's Sand Bird
Mario Royale
Koopa Car Chaos
MatPats shellmet display/storage
f a s t
Little Ant, Bigger Dreams!
1-1 but with a twist
